81 void UrsulaTask::loop()
82 {
83  ros::spinOnce();
84  double lastTime = ros::Time::now().toSec();
85 
86  ROS_INFO_STREAM(jointAnglesAct);
87  masterslave::UrsulaRCM rcmService;

91  tf::poseMsgToEigen(rcmService.response.trocar,RCM);
92 
93  masterslave::UrsulaDirectKinematics directKinematicsService;

95  directKinematicsService.request.jointAngles = jointAnglesActual;
96  directKinematicsClient.call(directKinematicsService);
97  directKinematicsService.request.jointAngles.clear();
98  tf::poseMsgToEigen(directKinematicsService.response.T_0_EE,TCP);

100 
101  boundingBox = std::move(std::unique_ptr<BoundingBox>(new BoundingBox(nh_,TCP,RCM.translation(),boundingBoxSize,rcmDistance)));
102 
103  ros::Rate rate(rosRate);
104 
105  while(ros::ok() && state == MOVE_TO_POSE)
106  {
107  ros::spinOnce();
108  cycleTime = ros::Time::now().toSec() - lastTime;
109  lastTime = ros::Time::now().toSec();
110  std_msgs::Float64 timeMsg;
111  timeMsg.data = cycleTime;
112  cycleTimePub.publish(timeMsg);
113  Eigen::Affine3d TCP_old = TCP;
114  // Hier muss der TCP-Service gecallt werden
115  masterslave::Manipulation manipulationService;
116  tf::poseEigenToMsg(TCP,manipulationService.request.T_0_EE_old);
117 
118  tcpClient.call(manipulationService);
119  tf::poseMsgToEigen(manipulationService.response.T_0_EE_new,TCP);
120  if(!TCP.isApprox(TCP_old) && boundingBox->checkBoundingBoxTCP(TCP))
121  {
122  masterslave::UrsulaInverseKinematics inverseKinematicsService;
123  tf::poseEigenToMsg(TCP,inverseKinematicsService.request.T_0_EE);
124  ROS_DEBUG_STREAM(inverseKinematicsService.request.T_0_EE.position);
125 
126  if(inverseKinematicsClient.call(inverseKinematicsService))
127  {
128  jointAnglesTar = Eigen::VectorXd::Map(inverseKinematicsService.response.jointAnglesTarget.data(),inverseKinematicsService.response.jointAnglesTarget.size());
129  }
130  }
131  else
132  {
133  masterslave::UrsulaDirectKinematics directKinematicsService;
134  std::vector<double> jointAnglesActual(jointAnglesAct.data(),jointAnglesAct.data()+jointAnglesAct.rows());
135  directKinematicsService.request.jointAngles = jointAnglesActual;
136  directKinematicsClient.call(directKinematicsService);
137  directKinematicsService.request.jointAngles.clear();
138  tf::poseMsgToEigen(directKinematicsService.response.T_0_EE,TCP);
139 
140  }
141 
142  commandVelocities();
143  rate.sleep();
144  }

155 void UrsulaTask::calcQ6()
156 {
157  jointAnglesAct.tail(3)(2) = (motorAngles(0) + motorAngles(1)) / 2;
158  if(fabs(motorAngles(0) + motorAngles(1))<0)

255 void UrsulaTask::commandVelocities()
256 {
257  double gripperVelocity;
258  std_msgs::Float64 Q4Vel, Q5Vel, Q6nVel, Q6pVel;
259  Q4Vel.data = (jointAnglesTar(7) - jointAnglesAct(7));
260  Q5Vel.data = (jointAnglesTar(8) - jointAnglesAct(8));
261  if(gripper_close && !gripper_open && !gripper_stop)
262  {
263  gripperVelocity = gripperVelocityValue;
264  }
265  else if(gripper_open && !gripper_close && !gripper_stop)
266  {
267  gripperVelocity = -gripperVelocityValue;
268  }
269  else
270  {
271  gripperVelocity = 0;
272  }
273 
274  Q6nVel.data = (jointAnglesTar(9)-jointAnglesAct(9));
275  Q6pVel.data = (jointAnglesTar(9)-jointAnglesAct(9));
276  // Stoppen der Greiferbacken, wenn eine der beiden am Anschlag ist, um Greiferöffnungswinkel nicht zu ändern
277  if(motorAngles(1)>=0.95*M_PI && (jointAnglesTar(9)-jointAnglesAct(9))>0)
278  {
279  Q6nVel.data = 0;
280  }
281  if(motorAngles(0)<=-0.95*M_PI && (jointAnglesTar(9)-jointAnglesAct(9))<0)
282  {
283  Q6pVel.data = 0;
284  }
285  Q6nVel.data += gripperVelocity;
286  Q6pVel.data -= gripperVelocity;
287 
288  Q4Pub.publish(Q4Vel);
289  Q5Pub.publish(Q5Vel);
290  Q6nPub.publish(Q6nVel);
291  Q6pPub.publish(Q6pVel);
292 
293  for(int i=0;i<7;i++)
294  {
295  std_msgs::Float64 jointAngleTemp;
296  jointAngleTemp.data = jointAnglesTar(i);
297  lbrJointAnglePub[i].publish(jointAngleTemp);
298  }
